==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Wych-elm
<hw>Wych"-elm`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[OE.
<ets>wiche</ets> a kind of elm, AS. <ets>wice</ets> a kind of tree. Cf.
<er>Wicker</er>.]</ety> <fld>(Bot.)</fld> <def>A species of elm
(<spn>Ulmus montana</spn>) found in Northern and Western Europe; Scotch
elm.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><note>⟦hand⟧ By confusion this word is often written
<xex>witch-elm</xex>.</note>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Wych-hazel</ent>⟦br⟧
